channel.title: Adam and Joe XFM
channel.description:
Adam Buxton and Joe Cornish first appeared on the London-only radio station XFM in 2003, leading to a series of popular podcasts. They remained at the station for three years, with their final show broadcast on Christmas Eve 2006.
